!</span><span class="users">1 User</span><img src="https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/spacer.gif" data-src="https://cdn.myanimelist.net/r/90x140/images/anime/2/75259.jpg?s=61d3b45b2e9c11cb2ed464453dc47b3c" data-srcset="https://cdn.myanimelist.net/r/90x140/images/anime/2/75259.jpg?s=61d3b45b2e9c11cb2ed464453dc47b3c 1x,https://cdn.myanimelist.net/r/180x280/images/anime/2/75259.jpg?s=615dfc1c653af50425bc8ab07f8850ea 2x" width="90" height="140" class="image lazyload" alt="Full Metal Panic!" border="0" ></a></li></ul></div></div></div>
